page.title: 16ECOLOGY
page.content: The best place to find out about rivers and streams is {LITTLE {AUSTRALIA},just off the main road to{ {GWEEK}. In this stream the water is fairly clean,but dirty in places. Eels,worms{ and other small insects live in and around the stream.It has a fairly slow current taking 11.6 minutes to travel 186m. The stream has an average depth of 15cm and an average width of 1.68m.The ground is damp nearly all year round and leaves cover the ground.This is a pleasant place to have lunch or simply a rest.
